title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 10PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 10PM” game were:
1-2-8-4
(one, two, eight, four)
